A copy of the amendment should be served upon the trustee, the bankruptcy administrator and any entity affected by the amendment. Upon completion of proper service, a certificate of service should immediately be filed with the court.A certificate of service indicating service of the notice of commencement of case, meeting of creditors and deadlines pursuant to Local Bankruptcy Rule 2002-1(a) has not been filed. The notice should be served on all creditors added after the original notice was given. Upon completion of proper service, a certificate of service should immediately be filed with the court.
